A 'user story' is a way of describing a product feature that helps specify who uses the feature, what it allows them to do in the product,
and what need or desire it satisfies.

FORMATS:

1.Connextra template
    As a <role> I can <capability>, so that <receive benefit>
              /* ex. " As a CFO, I can deploy cloud-based database so that finances are easy to manage.*/
              
2.'Hunting the value' alternative
   In order to <receive benefit> as a <role>, I can <goal/desire>
             /*ex. " In order to increase engagement of employees as HR Head, I can organise workshops.*/
          
3.Five Ws specific
   As <who> <when> <where>, I <want> because <why>
            /*ex. " As a gamer in my beginning stage professionally, I want a mentor for(because) tips and tricks.*/
